# This .gitignore file should be placed at the root of your Unity project directory.
#
# Get latest from https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Unity.gitignore
#
/[Ll]ibrary/
/[Tt]emp/
/[Oo]bj/
/[Bb]uild/
/[Bb]uilds/
/[Ll]ogs/
/[Uu]ser[Ss]ettings/
# MemoryCaptures can get excessive in size.
[Mm]emoryCaptures/
# AssetImportPipeline/ (comment out if you want to commit this folder)
#
# Optional: add other folders as needed
#
# Visual Studio cache directory
.vs/
#
# Visual Studio files
.suo
.user
.pidb
#
# Unity-generated files
*.unityproj
*.assetlink.json
*.booproj
*.sln.ide/
*.csproj
*.opendb
*.VC.db
#
# Packages
#
# exclude cache and various build results
/[Pp]ackages/obj/
/[Pp]ackages/Unity/
/[Pp]ackages/com.unity.testtools.codecoverage/
#
# Visual Scripting
/[Aa]ssets/VisualScripting.Generated/
#
# macOS files
.DS_Store*
#
# Windows files
Thumbs.db
#
# Linux files
#
# Built projects
/*.exe
/*.apk
/*.app
/*.unx
#
# Windows executable files
/*.exe.config
/*.pdb
/*.MDB
#
# Archives
/*.zip
/*.tar
/*.gz
#
# Output of the asset bundle build process.
/[Aa]ssets/[Aa]sset[Bb]undles/
#
# Autogenerated VS/Mac/Rider etc project file
# /[Aa]ssets/[Ss]cenes/[Ss]ample[Ss]cene.unity.meta (example of how to ignore a specific asset meta file)
#
# Example of ignoring a specific file in the ProjectSettings folder
# /[Pp]roject[Ss]ettings/ProjectSettings.asset
